io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.mod.registration

Class Colored<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.mod.registration.Colored<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the thing to register.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Registerable

    public class Colored<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Registerable
    A registerable that registers 16 things, one for each dye colour. This is done via Registerable.getNamedAdditionalRegisters() so the color names will be applied automatically.

      • getNamedAdditionalRegisters

        public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> getNamedAdditionalRegisters()
        Description copied from interface: Registerable
        Gets additional items that should be registered. Those may be Registerable, Items, Block TileEntities, Biomes ... The ones here may have a postfix. That allows to register multiple thing to the same registry. The new id is created from the id of this registerable, an underscore and the key in the map.
        Specified by:
        getNamedAdditionalRegisters in interface Registerable
